options are:
lba0
0x00	normal
0x01	short self-test
0x02	extended self-test
0x03	conveyance self-test
0x04	selective self-test
0x7f	abort off-line mode self-test routine
0x81	short self-test in captive mode
0x82	extended "
0x83	conveyance "
0x85	selective "
